Turkey May Promote Local Mobile Phone Production, Haberturk Says

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-02-21T06:32:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/turkey-may-promote-local-mobile-phone-production-haberturk-says.html
  Turkey  is considering diverting 20
percent of the annual revenue of the telecommunications
regulator to support local production of mobile phones,
Haberturk newspaper reported.  The 300 million liras ($190 million) annually from the
Information and Communication Technologies Authority in Ankara
would be used to promote hardware and software production in
Turkey, the newspaper said, citing draft plans from the
Communications Ministry.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
